Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathroom... bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,K... Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... Why is she sleeping like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,C... Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...my chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My "chance"? Kaoru's sleeping for Pete's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just low!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But... we {\i1}are{\i0} officially a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we took this trip so we can have some alone time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we are alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,at a hot-springs inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.09,0:01:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Jun'ichi coming over for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, how do I look right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel the blanket covering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can feel a draft in a few areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My yukata must be messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm probably exposed... in a few places!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Even with my eyes half open I can't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? H-Hey, Jun'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen?\N What's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just go with the flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that to be what I remember from this trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I did make sure to wear my favorite underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
