Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A monkey took my bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jun'ichi hand's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These kinds of memories don't come too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Jun'ichi.
